Package de.jvstvshd.localstream.network.util

Annotation Interface Deserializer.NoSerialize

Enclosing class:
Deserializer
@Target(FIELD) @Retention(RUNTIME) public static @interface Deserializer.NoSerialize
Marks a field non-(de)serializable.
Fields with this Annotation will not bes (de)serialized via Deserializer.deserialize(PacketBuffer, Class)
